params.fractionIds: The IDs of the fraction tokens

params.initialOwner: Address of the initial owner of the contract

params.fractionTokenURIs: An array of URIs for the fraction tokens metadata
params.originalId: The ID of the original token
params.totalPrice: The total price for all fractions combined

returns._0: The IDs of the newly minted fraction tokens

params.artistCommissionPercentage: The commission percentage for the artist
params.originalTokenURI: The URI of the original token metadata

returns._0: The ID of the newly minted original token

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.
